p style=\"text-align: center;\">阳江市老干部大学武当赵堡太极养生班团队与马朝中师兄在市老干部活动中心练功场合影</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/hd8.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/hd9.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">师父艾学林、陈国强与阳江市职业技术学院教职员工合影</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/hd10.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">陈国强教练与阳江市职业技术学院2017届太极拳一班合影</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/hd11.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">师父艾学林在阳江市妇女儿童活动中心为学员们上课</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/hd12.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/hd13.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/hd14.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">马朝中师兄带领武当赵堡太极拳生班学员练习武当赵堡太极拳</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/hd15.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"><br>陈国强教练在阳江市公安局灯光球场为民警上太极拳课</p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/hd16.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">陈国强教练在阳江市职业技术学院体育馆为教职员工上太极拳课</p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/hd17.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">陈国强教练在阳江市职业技术学院运动场为大学生上太极拳课</p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/hd18.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">陈国强教练在阳江市开放大学(原广播电视大学)为大学生上太极拳课</p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/08/23/f6f94563f3524b04a58a6ba898ae2903.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">阳江市老干部大学武当赵堡太极养生班团队在市老干部大学二十五周年志庆现场表演</p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/hd19.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">应邀参加阳江市绿洲瑜伽馆11周年志庆，现场太极拳表演</p><p><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/hd20.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA3.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/06/02/%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA4.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://jili20.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/article/2022/08/24/f5f3496a29b04d7fb1ce2ebdea3c7b12.jpg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" width=\"600\" data-display=\"inline\"><img src=\"https://jili20